                  , with intent to defraud his creditors
            </rs>, against the form of the statute.</p>
               <p>(Mr. 
               <persName id="t17791020-39-person459">
                  Richard
                   Dowding
               <interp inst="t17791020-39-person459" type="surname" value="Dowding"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17791020-39-person459" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
